version_description: Aoami’s work (http://tabs.ultimate-guitar.com/p/procol_harum/a_whiter_shade_of_pale_ver2_crd.htm).  I’ve simply added the chords to the lyrics for verse 2, choruses, and for the instrumentals for playing with auto-scroll..
This is different from most of the other renditions in that I have changed and added a lot more chords for a fuller presentation). Listen to the MP4 enclosed, it is actually quite easy to play.
Full instrumentals and easy to read, best played with acoustic guitar finger plucked, a superb tune from 67 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mb3iPP-tHdA.
